<view class='page'>
  <view class='box'>
    <view class='title-center'>
      <view class='text'>棚拍</view>
    </view>
    <view class='left-title'>特色:</view>
    <view class='content'>专业棚拍写真，馆内有专业宝宝引导师。</view>
    <view class='taocan'>套餐:</view>
    <view class='li'>1.提供精美服饰2套，可加一套自备服装</view>
    <view class='li'>2.提供宝宝小配饰，造型，道具等</view>
    <view class='li'>3.拍摄多种风格不同背景套组</view>
    <view class='li'>4.提供妈妈淡妆造型，拍摄选取5张精修母子合照（或一家三口）</view>
    <view class='li'>5.精修15张入册，底片全送</view>
    <view class='zengsong'>赠送:</view>
    <view class='ol'>赠送12寸琉璃水晶一体精美相册</view>
    <view class='ol'>韩式8寸白雕烤漆水晶摆台2个</view>
    <view class='price'>价格：16800 PESO</view>

    <view class='tip'>温馨提示</view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>1.多添加照片每张入册PHP350 </view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>2.拍摄前15天提前预约，不接受临时预约 </view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>3.拍摄后一周内通知选片 </view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>4.选片后20天内看排版设计，照会根据产品尺寸适当剪裁 </view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>5.同意发片后30天取件，如需加急，请提起前说明 </view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>6.超出套餐内容需遵守店内产品报价</view>
    <view class='tipcontent'>7.特殊节假日价格根据成本有浮动，价格以咨询报价为准 </view>
  </view>

  <view class='bottom-box'>
    <view class='title'>免费实拍体验</view>
    <view class='desc'>获得1对1体验试拍机会</view>
    <form bindsubmit="formSubmit">
      <view class='formclass'>
        <input name='name' placeholder='姓名' class='input'></input>
      </view>
      <view class='secondinput'>
        <input name='phonenum' placeholder='手机号' class='input'></input>
      </view>
      <button class="form-but" formType="submit">立即预约</button>
    </form>
    <button class="callme" bindtap='callme'>咨询热线：400-100-6053</button>
  </view>
  <view class='zhe' wx:if="{{show}}">
    <view class='zheBody'>
      <image src='/pages/image/qiqiu.png ' class='qiqiu'></image>
      <image src='/pages/image/gongxi.png ' class='gongxi'></image>
      <view class='zheMain'>
        <view class='zheMain-top'>恭喜您！预约成功</view>
        <view class='zheMain-bottom'>请保持手机通畅，我们会尽快与您取得联系！</view>
      </view>
      <view class='zhefooter' bindtap='ok'>
        知道了
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='ourtitlebox'>
    <image src='/pages/image/ourtitle.png' class='ourtitle'></image>
  </view>
</view>